42:38.556 --> 42:41.176
♪ From every part ♪

42:41.225 --> 42:44.895
♪ I can see those tears ♪

42:44.937 --> 42:47.687
♪ Every one is true ♪

42:47.732 --> 42:51.152
♪ When the door appears ♪

42:51.194 --> 42:53.404
♪ I’ll go right ♪

42:53.446 --> 42:59.156
♪ Through ♪

42:59.202 --> 43:01.502
- Part of being human
is finding the strength

43:01.537 --> 43:04.327
to fight through the obstacles
in your life.

43:04.373 --> 43:06.383
♪ ♪

43:06.417 --> 43:10.167
- ♪ I stand in liquid light ♪

43:10.213 --> 43:12.923
♪ Like everyone ♪

43:12.965 --> 43:16.835
♪ I built my life
with rhymes ♪

43:16.886 --> 43:18.386
♪ To carry on... ♪

43:18.429 --> 43:22.059
- While there are some
obstacles you cannot control,

43:22.100 --> 43:24.850
there are some you can.

43:24.894 --> 43:29.024
[electricity buzzing]

43:29.065 --> 43:32.155
- ♪ That one fine ♪

43:32.193 --> 43:37.033
♪ One fine day ♪

43:37.073 --> 43:38.413
- Like a little boy

43:38.449 --> 43:40.619
who wants to be friends
with an alien so badly,

43:40.660 --> 43:43.370
he is willing to trick
that alien’s enemy.

43:43.412 --> 43:45.542
♪ ♪

43:45.581 --> 43:48.501
[warbling]

43:50.962 --> 43:53.512
Max picked the right side.

43:55.258 --> 43:56.758
- No!

